      "description": "A honest, budget-friendly driver with strong project appeal. This car presents as a well-used but fundamentally capable platform, with a responsive engine, serviceable transmission, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it attractive to enthusiasts looking for an affordable entry point. It shows age cosmetically and will benefit from reconditioning, but it still offers solid bones, a complete package, and plenty of upside for someone who appreciates a straightforward machine with room to improve. Great candidate for a daily beater, weekend tinkering, or a value-minded build.",
